freenet.io
Class AddressIdentifier

java.lang.Object
  freenet.io.AddressIdentifier

public class AddressIdentifier
extends Object

Identifies numeric IP addresses. This class is currently capable of recognizing:

  • IPv4 unabridged (a.b.c.d)
  • IPv4 abridged (a.b.d or a.d)
  • IPv6 unabridged (a:b:c:d:e:f:g:h)
